{{!
  CHARGEN CUSTOM TABS SNIPPET

  Adds the "Secret & Goal" tab to the chargen step list.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/components/chargen-custom-tabs.hbs

  IMPORTANT: This file contains the other chargen step tabs (Demographics, Groups, Abilities, etc.)
  Your job is to add the Secrets & Goals tab to the existing list.

  STEP 1: Open your game's ares-webportal/app/components/chargen-custom-tabs.hbs

  STEP 2: Find the existing <ul class="nav nav-tabs"> with other <li> tab entries
  (you should see Demographics, Groups, Abilities, Background, RP Hooks, Profile Icon, etc.)

  STEP 3: Copy the <li> below and paste it at the END of that <ul>, right before </ul>:

  ---START COPY HERE---
  <li role="presentation" class="nav-item"><a href="#chargen-inklings-pane" aria-controls="chargen-inklings-pane" role="tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" class="nav-link">Secret &amp; Goal</a></li>
  ---END COPY---

  IMPORTANT DETAILS:

  BOOTSTRAP VERSION:
  - Use data-bs-toggle="tab" (Bootstrap 5)
  - NOT data-toggle="tab" (that's Bootstrap 4 - won't work)

  ID MATCHING:
  - The href="#chargen-inklings-pane" MUST match the id="chargen-inklings-pane" in chargen-custom.snippet.hbs
  - Do NOT change this value

  PLACEMENT:
  - This <li> must go INSIDE the existing <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
  - Do NOT create a separate <ul> for this tab
  - It should be on the same level as Demographics, Groups, Abilities, etc.

  IF YOU CUSTOMIZED chargen_required_types:
  If your game uses different inkling types, change the tab label to match.
  Example: if chargen_required_types: [hooks], change "Secret &amp; Goal" to "Hooks"

  BEFORE (secret and goal):
    <a href="#chargen-inklings-pane" ... class="nav-link">Secret &amp; Goal</a>

  AFTER (hooks):
    <a href="#chargen-inklings-pane" ... class="nav-link">Hooks</a>

  Note: Keep href="#chargen-inklings-pane" and id="chargen-inklings-pane" the same,
        only change the display label to match your configured types.
}}
